<br>
I leveled, off and on from 23-35 like this, and still sometimes use the method at 40(only instead of pet, use a warrior/pally/sk, they deal lots more damage)<br>
<br>
The &quot;dead zones&quot; that i used for this are near the giant fort in FM(to the right, by the rock), and in front of the pillars that go down to the underwater gobbo zone.  This worked great, and i don't think i ever died to a mob this way.<br>
<br>
Edit: thanks for the charm post, that gives me a new insight on my underused charm line.<br>
