<br>
Several innaccuracies...<br>
<br>
<br>
#1 Pet only takes half of exp if you don't do ANY damage to it.<br>
#2 Pet takes 33.3% EXP unless you do 50% or more of damage.<br>
<br>
Okay, in EW I found that charming a Kromriff Guardsman, giving it two weps... and using your best haste spell is the way to go.  Then go out into the wandering area of eastern wastes, slow all mobs, and mow them down.  Each guardsmen you charm is worth about 20 mobs....  he tears em up that fast.  I was able to get several levels in EW in merely hours...<br>
<br>
The charm dual wield (optional) haste, slow method is more effective at high levels for me.  I have charm solo'd all the way up through PoN to PoV...  <br>
